Question: Diketahui matriks $A = \begin{pmatrix} 2 & 1 \\ 3 & 4 \end{pmatrix}$ dan $B = \begin{pmatrix} -1 & 2 \\ 0 & 1 \end{pmatrix}$. Tentukan hasil perkalian matriks $A \times B$.
Answer: $\begin{pmatrix} -2 & 5 \\ -3 & 10 \end{pmatrix}$
Explanation: Perkalian matriks baris dikali kolom. Elemen (1,1) = $2(-1) + 1(0) = -2$. Elemen (1,2) = $2(2) + 1(1) = 5$. Elemen (2,1) = $3(-1) + 4(0) = -3$. Elemen (2,2) = $3(2) + 4(1) = 10$.
