  - Text: $\begin{pmatrix} -2 & -3 \\ 5 & 10 \end{pmatrix}$
  - Text: $\begin{pmatrix} 5 & -2 \\ 10 & -3 \end{pmatrix}$
  - Text: $\begin{pmatrix} 1 & 3 \\ 3 & 5 \end{pmatrix}$
  - Text: $\begin{pmatrix} -2 & 10 \\ -3 & 5 \end{pmatrix}$
